_do-convert-metadata - Convert Single Metadata

USAGE:
    _do-convert-metadata <metadata-file>

DESCRIPTION:
    Convert metadata for a single video file. Updates the metadata
    format to the current standard. Internal tool used by
    _convert-metadata.

ARGUMENTS:
    metadata-file
        Path to the metadata file to convert

NOTE:
    This is an internal tool and typically not called directly.

EXAMPLES:
    _do-convert-metadata /path/to/metadata/file
